@node "Introduction" "Introduction:"


     @{b}Conversion@{ub}

        Conversion is a commodity that converts Metric units to English units
or vice versa.  Being a commodity, it is expecially useful because you just
pop it up when you need it and hide it when you are done.

        I thought up the idea because a lot of times I'm talking to other
people in diffrent parts of the world, and they will tell me something like
"I'm 1.8 Meters tall", and I will tell them "I'm 6 feet tall", leaving us both
slightly baffled, until we look it up in a book or something... You may find
your own use for the program.  If you do, and you have suggestions on how the
program might better serve you, let me know.
@endnode

